com.mostc.pftt.telemetry
Class PhptTestResult

java.lang.Object
  com.mostc.pftt.telemetry.PhptTestResult

public class PhptTestResult
extends java.lang.Object

result of running a PhptTestCase the status of PhptTestCase is determined by: -executing SKIPIF section(optional) -comparing the actual and EXPECT, EXPECTF or EXPECTREGEX sections -certain sections(ENV, STDIN) if present, are skipped for HTTP testing

Author:
Matt Ficken
